def color_diagonal_lines_black(input_grid: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:
    output = np.copy(input_grid)
    n = input_grid.shape[0]
    for i in range(n):
        output[i, i] = black
        output[i, n - i - 1] = black
    return output
